commit cffcfba3d9b12b43a6a32c842bc4ee02eec8bd67
Author: Jean A. Senellart <jean.senellart@systrangroup.com>
Date:   Fri Oct 6 23:44:24 2017 +0200

    Introduce documentation version selection
---
 docs/css/version-select.css | 16 +++++++++++++
